def comparePriceChanges(cutoff):
    before = stock_prices.loc[cutoff]/stock_prices.loc['2012-06-01']
    after = stock_prices.loc['2017-06-01']/stock_prices.loc[cutoff]
    plt.scatter(before, after)
    plt.xlabel('Price Change Before ' + cutoff)
    plt.ylabel('Price Change After ' + cutoff)
    plt.title('Comparing Fund Price Changes Over the Past 5 Years')
